'''Statuary Park''' was located on the grounds of the [[Bakur Memorial Building|Bakur Complex]] within the [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Salis D'aar/Legends|Salis D'aar]] on [[Bakura/Legends|Bakura]]. This large area of land was filled with statues that portrayed both people and events in Bakura's past. The location was also filled with [[namana]] [[Tree/Legends|trees]] and neatly cut shrubs. Visitors would often feel that the [[Statuary]] Park was unusually remote despite the fact that they were in the center of the city. Its circular shape covered roughly half the same surface area as the [[Bakur Memorial Building]].

